import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import routers from './routers'
import './styles/index.css'

Vue.use(VueRouter)

Vue.config.productionTip = false

const router = new VueRouter({
  mode: 'history',
  routes: routers
})

new Vue({
  el: '#app',
  router,
  render: h => h(App)
})
